column5: Looking for a recommendation for a drive in lodge near Wawa for a possible late September trip. Looking for housekeeping plan. Nothing fancy but decent Walleye fishing. Thanks
send me an email I'll get a place for u,you bring your own boat?
Check your PM as I sent you some info.
go to noto.net, there are 100's of outfitters on there
If you find a good place near wawa. let me know.
